.TH merl_transform 3 "syntax_tools 4.0.3" "Ericsson AB" "Erlang Module Definition"
.SH NAME
merl_transform \- Parse transform for merl.

.SH DESCRIPTION
.PP
Enables the use of automatic metavariables and using quasi-quotes in matches and case switches. Also optimizes calls to functions in \fImerl\fR by partially evaluating them, turning strings to templates, and so on, at compile-time.

.PP
Using \fI-include_lib("syntax_tools/include/merl.hrl").\fR enables this transform, unless the macro \fIMERL_NO_TRANSFORM\fR is defined first.

.SH FUNCTIONS
.LP
